About this Cursor
All
Introducing the Castle Crashers Custom Cursor Pack, featuring an adorable Peasant character as your Windows cursor. This fanart-inspired cursor pack is perfect for gamers and art enthusiasts who love to add a touch of whimsy to their digital world. The Peasant character, with its non-elemental magical attacks and starting weapon, the Wooden Spoon, adds a playful twist to your cursor collection. Inspired by the popular game Castle Crashers' color palette, this pack will surely become a favorite among creative users looking for unique cursors. Interestingly, the Peasant was an essential member of medieval farming communities and often played a crucial role in historical events.
