Research. Technology. Nature.
The number of seconds past the minute that you got out of bed.
The people that you share your tube car with on a Thursday morning.
The exact number of milk bottles in that Haribo bag.
All these things look completely random.
Except they aren’t.
Most of the events that we navigate through every day are easy to predict and recreate. A knowledgeable private detective armed with statistics and Internet access can track your life to the tiniest detail without ever needing to follow you.
But there’s something that depends on randomness and unpredictability a thousand times more than your private life (in fact, because of that, it does too).
It is your online security.
Behind 5 of every 10 security protocol attacks stands a weak random number generator.
You may use the strongest ever encryption, 2FA, and be 100% GDPR-compliant when dealing with personal data, but low quality of random numbers used in your security ecosystem can compromise the whole thing.
Entropy on Tap is a source of truly random numbers.
We pull entropy from a multitude of natural sources to provide the highest quality random numbers for your security applications. Our random numbers are unpredictable and irreversible. Our generators are non-cloneable and protected from outside influence.
Read more about our innovative approach.
For Businesses
Decrease your attack surface by switching your day-to-day random number generation matters to Entropy on Tap.
For Security Vendors
Generate amazingly strong cryptographic keys at a fraction of hardware solution costs.
